:New for Wheezy
  * Security hardening build flags
  * /run
  * Stop using Video4Linux ver. 1
  * Stop using /dev/dsp on Linux\n...

= Wheezy の Release Goal

:New for Wheezy
  * ((*Security hardening build flags*))
  * /run
  * Stop using Video4Linux ver. 1
  * Stop using /dev/dsp on Linux\n...

= Security hardening build flags

* パッケージ構築時に
  セキュリティを強化するコンパイルフラグを(デフォルトで)有効に
  → stable がより頑健に!!
  * Format string checks
  * D_FORTIFY_SOURCE
  * Stack protector
  * Read-only relocations

= Wheezy の Release Goal

:New for Wheezy
  * Security hardening build flags
  * ((*/run*))
  * Stop using Video4Linux ver. 1
  * Stop using /dev/dsp on Linux\n...

= /run

* boot の早い段階で一時ディレクトリを用意
  * /var/run → /run
  * /var/lock → /run/lock
  * /dev/shm → /run/shm
  * /tmp → /run/tmp\n...

